text: An olive branch is a branch of the olive tree, often used symbolically. Olive Branch may also refer to: *Olive Branch, Illinois *Olive Branch, Kentucky *Olive Branch, Mississippi **Olive Branch Airport *Olive Branch, North Carolina *Olive Branch, Ohio *The Olive Branch, a magazine *HMS Olive Branch *Operation Olive Branch, code-name of the second Turkish military intervention in Syria starting in January 2018.
title: Olive Branch (disambiguation)
